data.description: Experience coastal living in this stunning tri-level oceanfront abode boasting unobstructed panoramic views from every floor. Renovated and lovingly maintained, this home offers a seamless blend of modern updates and timeless charm. Conveniently located just a short drive away to Windward Mall, indulge in the convenience of shopping and dining options, while being within easy reach of the technicolor sunrise, serene coral reefs, and the inviting sands of Kaneohe Bay's Sand Bar. Immerse yourself in the serene rhythm of ocean life as you envision washing dishes against the backdrop of endless blue vistas and waking up to the gentle glow of sunrise dancing across the horizon. Don't miss this rare opportunity to make everyday moments extraordinary in this oceanfront oasis. *This is an OWNER-OCCUPIED property - please give 24hr notice before requesting showings*
